似乎只能找到这两处，但是它是默认开启的？# Order in which entity providers should be used [default: [theoneprobe:entity.default], [theoneprobe:entity.debug], [theoneprobe:entity.entity], [topaddons:ic2], [topaddons:base], [topaddons:botania], [topaddons:forestry], [topaddons:stevescarts], [topaddons:storagedrawers], [topaddons:tconstruct], [topaddons:vanilla]]
